tora-san , the expert ( 男はつらいよ &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; otoko wa tsurai yo : hana mo arashi mo torajirō ) is a 1982 japanese comedy film directed by yoji yamada . it stars kiyoshi atsumi as torajirō kuruma ( tora-san ) , and yuko tanaka as his love interest or " madonna " . tora-san , the expert is the &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; entry in the popular , long-running otoko wa tsurai yo series . this became the first tora-san film to be released on dvd with english subtitles in 16:9 ratio when the hong kong label panorama did so in 2006 .